name: Ranks4time
tagline: This is my plugin for minecraft bukkit servers that when some people have played for a certain time they get a certain rank so this is automatic and no need for ranking via PEX or GM.
body:
Hey guys! Please note that this is my first plugin and I will be needing some help whether your a good coder or amazing as when I grow fond of java and bukkit API I will need somebody of my standard or better to teach me more that I can't learn on my own or just as somebody to go through it with me and be the person that not just sits there pointing out errors and making more ideas but coding themselves :)


Please check up every so often for more updates and more features :)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
